'''[[Nepal]]''' contains part of the [[Himalayas]], the highest [[mountain range]] in the world. Eight of the fourteen [[eight-thousander]]s are located in the country, either in whole or shared across a border with [[China]] or [[India]]. Nepal has the highest mountain in the world, [[Mount Everest]].

